Usage:

  Create a signal

  $> ubus-signal /var/ipc/user/name/application/signalname

  Listen to a signal

  $> ubus-listen /var/ipc/user/name/application/signalname
  

  Create a method

  $> ubus-method /var/ipc/user/name/application/methodname

  Call a method

  $> echo "test" | ubus-call /var/ipc/user/name/application/methodname
  
